svg.desc:
Yearly Calendar
Click on any month to view just the month, click on the month title to view the entire year
Defaults to the current year, but can be changed Append a 4 digit year to the url of the SVG image, i.e. calendar.svg?year=2000
For a month calendar, pass a number 1-12 as the month, i.e. calendar.svg?month=2
Both parameters can be passed, i.e. calendar.svg?month=2&year=2000
Jay Nick STEAMcoded.org
